snippet.title: WTF: Work Time Fun Gameplay (PSP)
snippet.description: Raw gameplay of Work Time Fun, known in Japan as Baito Hell 2000, a video game developed by D3 and Sony for the PlayStation Portable. The English title is a play on the slang "WTF", short for 'What The Fuck?', indicating confusion. WTF was released in Japan on December 22, 2005, and in America on October 17, 2006.
